{"id":"129e9d55-7b66-4ca3-ba63-423786f769e0","name":"Johnny Cage","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(103, 103, 103);\">Johnny Cage</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Mortal Kombat 1</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Create your own scenario</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/GSDMVVfqh95U33cwPBteb.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Merry Christmas everyone 🎄</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/HqgZmXUqSWPvUCfCYh3YP.webp\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Like many stars before him, Johnny became addicted to his fame. He came to measure his self-worth by his fans' adoration and their praise of him on social media. But with his star now fading, Johnny is fighting an uphill battle to remain relevant. He joins Liu Kang's Earthrealm champions hoping that it will provide his career and his fame a desperately needed boost.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/f0kBjUxhL56muXxHgIYzW.webp\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"cf810101-3bd5-42cb-a56f-67818bbf6c90_c8cfb1c1-0d6f-41fb-9254-b087fbb83455.webp","creator":"Midnight Kitten","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🎮 Game","🦸 Hero","🌗 Switch"],"chats":967,"messages":34821,"created_at":"2024-12-25T10:32:24.741704+00:00"}